{"name":"Hammerhand","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Imbuing his muscles with psychic force, the psyker brings down the wrath of the Emperor of Mankind in powerful strikes that shatter ceramite and plasteel.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Imbue self and allies with Unnatural Strength","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 3","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker selects a number of allies within range equal to his psy rating (which may include the psyker). While the power persists, the affected characters gain the Unnatural Strength (X) trait where X is equal to the user&rsquo;s psy rating, or increases their existing trait&rsquo;s value by 4. This benefit ends if a character moves out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"AwHxyC8aetgkgizz"}
{"name":"Purge Soul","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Using the corruption in his target&rsquo;s soul as kindling, the psyker ignites an inner fire, burning away the target&rsquo;s tainted soul.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Target foe using Willpower","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 35","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker chooses a target within range and line of sight, who opposes the power with a Willpower test. If the psyker wins the Opposed test, the target suffers 1 point of Energy damage per degree of success on the test, plus an amount equal to the target&rsquo;s Corruption bonus, ignoring armour and Toughness bonus.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"HAGKoNV6whr5lsKJ"}
{"name":"Psychic Communion","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Establishing a psychic link with his allies, the psyker ensures that they act in concert, the better to deliver righteous judgement on the Emperor&rsquo;s foes.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Increase Initiative  for self and allies","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Perception 35","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker selects a number of allies up to psy rating within range. While the power persists, the psyker and his affected allies add +2 to their Initiative. This can change an already established Initiative order.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"IF3h5LD4IXIuYizB"}
{"name":"Sanctuary","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker summons a barrier of holy force, pushing back the Daemon and deflecting the blows of heretics</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Allies gain force field protection","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 45","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"Self","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker selects a number of allies up to psy rating (which may include the psyker) within 10 metres x psy rating. For the duration of the power, each affected character benefits from a force field with a protection rating of 5 x PR and no overload chance. In addition, Daemons must pass a Challenging (+0) Willpower test in order to move toward an affected character.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"WCIx4OlHkVNx4Tuh"}
{"name":"Word of the Emperor","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker speaks with the very voice of the Emperor, causing his enemies to cringe in pain and terror. Bolstering his denunciations and catechisms of hate with psychic resonance, the psyker ensures that heretics and Daemons must struggle past his holy words in order to lay hand or claw upon him.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Enemies suffer penalties to attack user","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Fellowship 30","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>Whilst the power remains in effect, whenever a character within range takes an Attack action targeting the psyker, the attacker must pass a Challenging (+0) Willpower test or suffer a &ndash;5 penalty to his attack roll for each degree of failure.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"XSvP00UKpcHzAJNG"}
{"name":"Cleansing Flame","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker projects his purity in a great gout of holy flames. The azure fires burn hotter than any mundane flame, blazing with the righteousness of the Emperor. Heretics and Daemons cannot hope to stand against the purifying flame.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Target enemies withHoly damage","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy raging 4","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10+PR+WPB","penetration":"","special":"Flame, Sanctified, Spray, DMG+WPB"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"cmXqTiCfc3j8L17g"}
{"name":"Banishment","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Speaking words of banishment, the psyker draws on his faith and reaches out to sever the cords tying a Daemon to reality. Its hold in realspace broken, the Daemon is cast back into the depths of the Warp.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Hurl daemonic target back into the Warp","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 3","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-20,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker selects a target in range and line of sight, which must possess the Warp Instability trait. The targeted Daemon must immediately make a Willpower test, with a &ndash;5 penalty for each degree of success on the Focus Power test. The target suffers 1 point of Energy damage per degree of failure on the test, ignoring Toughness bonus and armour. If this would deal damage equal to or in excess of the target&rsquo;s remaining wounds, it is immediately cast back into the Warp.&nbsp;</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"ixry0ZClDZLIz3kT"}
{"name":"Holocaust","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The psyker ignites his very soul in a devastating conflagration that washes out from him in all directions. It is said that the flames of this power burn not only flesh, but the very souls of the psyker&rsquo;s enemies, destroying them utterly&mdash;and that the psyker risks consuming his own soul in the process.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Burn surrounding enemies withWarpfire","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 5","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-20,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"Self","sustained":"Full Action","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"<p>Each round the psyker sustains Holocaust, he emits a psychic blast centred on himself. He is not affected by the blast, but each turn the psyker sustains the power he suffers 1d10+psy rating Energy damage, ignoring armour and Toughness bonus.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"1d10*PR","penetration":"0","special":"Blast (PR), Flame, Warp Weapon"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"jyuy6gfqV2S5DZOS"}
{"name":"Exorcism","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Many psykers who follow the path of Daemonology know that the best weapons against the Daemon are faith and psychic powers; only with the energies of the Warp is it truly possible to fight the Warp. Bolstering his ritual with psychic current, the psyker prepares to exorcise a Daemon.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Inflict damage on Daemon","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 40","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"Half Action","subtype":"Attack, Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker selects a single target character with the Daemonic trait, which opposes the power with a Willpower test. If the psyker wins the opposed test, the character suffers Willpower damage equal to the user&rsquo;s psy rating for each degree of success on the psyker&rsquo;s test.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/gothic-cross.svg","effects":[],"_id":"yQmPNStp175QKPR4"}
